{"tid":331503,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"目標：五年內抵制大型補習社","createTime":"2017-07-22T08:40:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T10:39:11.000Z","uid":20848,"like":78,"dislike":167,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3821ec78f202973da0da39cc35f6aa2bafe94f93","tid":331503,"uid":20848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T08:40:24.000Z","msg":"Yo巴打們，幾個月前都開過post話搞緊D野幫下中學生，抵制大型補習社、名師效應等不良風氣！簡單講多次我嘅理念，大型補習社好多都係<strong>video class</strong>，而且<strong>大班教學，毫無彈性</strong>，而且仲要<strong>越黎越貴</strong>。相反香港嘅elearning落後不前，連大陸都係短短3,4年發展到咁大，但香港仲停留係<strong>20年前嘅補習模式</strong>，所以我好想做D野，改變呢個風氣，或者去令呢D大型補習社反思下點樣去進步。<br />\n<br />\n今日我地終於成立左<strong><ins>AfterSchool</ins></strong>，係由一班大學生、退休老師發起嘅組織。我地會定期提供：<br />\n<ul><br />\n<li><strong>實用溫習、考試技巧</strong>，助你提升學習效率</li><br />\n<li>歷界DSE狀元傳授<strong>讀書心得</strong></li><br />\n<li><strong>免費網上課程</strong>，幫你極速重溫抽象概念、熟悉考試常見題型</li><br />\n<li>1on1為你提供<strong>選科意見</strong>，分析各個選擇嘅利幣</li><br />\n</ul><br />\n<br />\n我地而家主要透過以下三個途徑去為學生提供服務：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Instagram Page</strong><br />\n<ul><br />\n<li>每日更新DSE資訊、讀書技巧等，睇IG之餘仲可以幫埋你溫習！</li><br />\n<li>可以按此follow<a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/afterschool_hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fafterschool_hk&d=wOaQs7LDeACPKjJEbkFVUzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=29c5b802\" target=\"_blank\">www.instagram.com/afterschool_hk</a>，或在IG上搜尋 afterschool_hk</li><br />\n</ul><br />\n<strong>WhatsApp群組</strong><br />\n<ul><br />\n<li>有超過十個來自唔同學系嘅大學生同老師坐陣，助你解決任何科目嘅問題！</li><br />\n<li>推動討論同學術氣氛，鼓勵同學互相幫忙互相學習。</li><br />\n<li>歡迎其他有心老師或大學生加入！</li><br />\n<li>有興趣加入嘅可以tg我 <a href=\"https://t.me/ronaldtse28\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fronaldtse28&d=wOaQs7LDeACPKjJEbkFVUzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=447732b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ronaldtse28</a></li><br />\n</ul><br />\n<strong>Blog</strong><br />\n<ul><br />\n<li>定期發放學術性文章、讀書技巧、歷界DSE同學嘅心得分享</li><br />\n<li>歡迎老師同學投稿</li><br />\n<li>網站係 <a href=\"http://www.afterschoolcommunity.com/blog\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.afterschoolcommunity.com%2Fblog&d=wOaQs7LDeACPKjJEbkFVUzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=3fd6e377\" target=\"_blank\">www.afterschoolcommunity.com/blog</a></li><br />\n</ul><br />\n另外都好想覺位巴打幫手諗下，點樣先可以比更多學生得到呢D資源同資訊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n感激！"},{"pid":"e169923e54e7b48de7a112c442f41e23420034cf","tid":331503,"uid":649,"like":63,"dislike":0,"score":63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T08:50:29.000Z","msg":"利弊唔係利幣"},{"pid":"5b77cb004ea914e1c84e91e5760e555ed9336ac2","tid":331503,"uid":92743,"like":33,"dislike":4,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T08:51:45.000Z","msg":"你地咪又係收錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30a1edb0858f26b96a81bd7b8b6a514f1d1c55d1","tid":331503,"uid":20848,"like":9,"dislike":8,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T09:03:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你地咪又係收錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家已經開始左第一個免費online course, 雖然得2X個學生，但我地相信我地會慢慢擴大我地嘅影響力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9857fc5b6ae25aa97ce6aeb8a224e76ab5303538","tid":331503,"uid":20848,"like":0,"dislike":18,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T09:03:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>利弊唔係利幣</blockquote><br />\n中文太差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0a018bba32f1064206d554ebbc54d287f3b4a25","tid":331503,"uid":186,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T09:30:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你地咪又係收錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5719049c3a22dfcae7f292b46fff5eab0d33efc","tid":331503